The [[Bayer designation]] '''Omicron Centauri''' (ο Cen / ο Centauri) is shared by two star systems, in the constellation [[Centaurus]]: * [[Omicron¹ Centauri|ο¹ Centauri]] * [[Omicron² Centauri|ο² Centauri]] They are separated by 0.07° on the sky. They may be physically related.
